        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Method",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Make the dough",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Preheat the oven to 190°C fan. Line a baking tray with baking paper. Whisk together the {{plain-flour}}, {{baking-powder}}, {{mixed-spice}}, and {{sea-salt-fine}}. Rub in the cold {{unsalted-butter}} with your fingertips until the mixture resembles breadcrumbs. Stir in the {{caster-sugar}}, {{dried-currants}}, and {{mixed-peel}}. Add the beaten {{eggs}} and {{whole-milk}} and mix until the dough just comes together. It will be soft but not sticky.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "heading",
        "attrs": {
          "level": 3
        },
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Shape, top, and bake, 18 to 20 minutes",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "text": "Divide the dough into 8 equal portions and shape each into a thick, domed round of about 7 cm directly on the lined tray. Press the {{glace-cherries}} and {{blanched-almonds}} firmly into the surface of each one: this is the ",
            "type": "text"
          },
          {
            "text": "fat rascal",
            "type": "text",
            "marks": [
              {
                "type": "glossaryTooltip",
                "attrs": {
                  "termId": "cmp9ytzrg0000fwv4xyku0q8p"
                }
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "text": " topping. Press hard enough that the topping is embedded, not just resting on the surface. Bake for 18 to 20 minutes until the tops are dry and the bases are coloured. Cool on a rack for at least 10 minutes before eating.",
            "type": "text"
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
